[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "This is starting to get spooky..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 19.0,
    "text": "What are you doing in my house?!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.0,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "Oh thanks Mr. Robinson, I knew I could rely on you to wake me up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.0,
    "endTime": 23.0,
    "text": "I can't be late for Miss Simeon's class again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.0,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "I've already been late the ones this week."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "Well three times if you count the other two times."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "So I can't let her catch me again or she'll give me detention."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "And there's no way she's gonna catch me this time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 31.0,
    "text": "I mean, it's not like I'm doing it on purpose."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 33.0,
    "text": "I'm just a heavy sleeper, you know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.0,
    "endTime": 35.0,
    "text": "I mean, you wouldn't want to be woken up at 7am, would you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "I mean, you would because you're old."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.0,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "What is it with old people and getting up this early?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "I guess you're just trying to drag out the last few days of life you got left."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "Anyways, have a nice day, bye!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "Wait!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.0,
    "endTime": 49.0,
    "text": "Wait, wait!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.0,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "Hey, stop little boy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.0,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "I need to borrow your..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "Yes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "I need to borrow your wheels."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 57.0,
    "text": "Let me in!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.0,
    "endTime": 58.0,
    "text": "Rocky!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 59.0,
    "text": "Open the door!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.0,
    "endTime": 59.0,
    "text": "Let me in!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Rocky!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 61.0,
    "text": "Rocky!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.0,
    "endTime": 62.0,
    "text": "Rocky, let me in!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "Wow, it really does sound like trash."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 65.0,
    "text": "Open the door!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "Three, two, one..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "And so begins my ten second countdown."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.0,
    "endTime": 76.0,
    "text": "Ten, nine, eight..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.0,
    "endTime": 76.0,
    "text": "Wait!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.0,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "Seven, six, five..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "Three, two, one..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 88.0,
    "text": "You're late!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.0,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "Detention!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.0,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "Home time, everyone!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 99.0,
    "text": "Except you, Waterson."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.0,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "I'll see you back here in five."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "Oh, hey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 107.0,
    "text": "Too bad about the detention."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.0,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Nah, it's alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "I got this annoying breathing technique that's gonna make it as hard for her as it is for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.0,
    "endTime": 116.0,
    "text": "Cool story, Gumball."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.0,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.0,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "Who said that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 118.0,
    "text": "Me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "Whoa, Clayton!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "You're disguised as a water fountain?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "Yeah, well, nothing interesting ever happens to me, so I thought I'd try becoming inanimate objects."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "And, spoiler alert, nothing interesting ever happens to them either."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "Samantha, finally!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "We've been waiting so long, Angela's clothes are back in fashion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.0,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "Oh, that one's pretty interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 144.0,
    "text": "Yeah, it wasn't the ball."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.0,
    "endTime": 145.0,
    "text": "See?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "It's boring."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.0,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "We're not all like you, Gumball, running around, stopping the school from being blown up, or wrestling an alligator."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "I don't think he's ever wrestled an alligator."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 155.0,
    "text": "Let the boy finish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.0,
    "endTime": 156.0,
    "text": "I'm finished."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.0,
    "endTime": 156.0,
    "text": "Fair enough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.0,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "Dude, you're wasting your talent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 161.0,
    "text": "If nothing cool happens to you, why not just change into someone else?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 165.0,
    "text": "If I've learned one thing from movies, it's that the key to happiness is never be yourself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 167.0,
    "text": "Okay, then I'll be Darwin!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.0,
    "endTime": 170.0,
    "text": "So, what are we gonna do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.0,
    "endTime": 172.0,
    "text": "I do not sound like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.0,
    "endTime": 173.0,
    "text": "Try clearing your throat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.0,
    "endTime": 174.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.0,
    "endTime": 177.0,
    "text": "Oh, yeah, that's better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.0,
    "endTime": 181.0,
    "text": "Look, look, no offense, but he's kind of the sidekick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.0,
    "endTime": 184.0,
    "text": "If you want real excitement, you gotta aim a little higher."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.0,
    "endTime": 187.0,
    "text": "You know, someone a little more awesome?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.0,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "You know, someone who's a little bit..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "Me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "You can be me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.0,
    "endTime": 194.0,
    "text": "That's more like it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.0,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "What is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.0,
    "endTime": 196.0,
    "text": "Get in here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.0,
    "endTime": 196.0,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.0,
    "endTime": 198.0,
    "text": "I could sit your detention for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.0,
    "endTime": 201.0,
    "text": "Well, aren't you gonna stop him?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "It's not right that he should be taking your punishment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 207.0,
    "text": "Oh, Clayton, no, please don't sit my detention for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 208.0,
    "text": "It'll be a really bad idea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "I mean, he couldn't hear me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "I tried."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 211.0,
    "text": "I tried hard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.0,
    "endTime": 217.0,
    "text": "Wait, if Clayton was a water fountain, then I must have been drinking..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.0,
    "endTime": 220.0,
    "text": "Come on, let's go before Simeon catches the real me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.0,
    "endTime": 226.0,
    "text": "Good morning, kids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.0,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 232.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.0,
    "endTime": 235.0,
    "text": "Hey, guys, it's me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.0,
    "endTime": 237.0,
    "text": "Yeah, and it's us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.0,
    "endTime": 241.0,
    "text": "Just out of interest, Rocky, how many of us can you see?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.0,
    "endTime": 243.0,
    "text": "No, it's me, Clayton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.0,
    "endTime": 244.0,
    "text": "I'm doing like you said."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.0,
    "endTime": 245.0,
    "text": "Now I'm Rocky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.0,
    "endTime": 246.0,
    "text": "Dude, you can't drive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.0,
    "endTime": 248.0,
    "text": "Oh, can't I?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 251.0,
    "text": "Gumball, you started this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.0,
    "endTime": 252.0,
    "text": "You have to stop it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.0,
    "endTime": 257.0,
    "text": "But how do you stop somebody when they could be anybody, anything, anything?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.0,
    "endTime": 258.0,
    "text": "You just don't want to do it, do you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.0,
    "endTime": 259.0,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.0,
    "endTime": 260.0,
    "text": "Who are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.0,
    "endTime": 261.0,
    "text": "I'm..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.0,
    "endTime": 262.0,
    "text": "I'm Doctor..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.0,
    "endTime": 263.0,
    "text": "Doctor..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.0,
    "endTime": 264.0,
    "text": "Man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.0,
    "endTime": 267.0,
    "text": "Here to do doctoring things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.0,
    "endTime": 268.0,
    "text": "The stethoscope isn't even in his ears."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.0,
    "endTime": 269.0,
    "text": "He's clearly cl..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.0,
    "endTime": 271.0,
    "text": "Hey, guys, it's me, Clayton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.0,
    "endTime": 272.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry about the bad driving."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.0,
    "endTime": 274.0,
    "text": "But you gotta admit, it was fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.0,
    "endTime": 278.0,
    "text": "Oh, Doctor Man, we've got a couple of patients we need you to attend to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.0,
    "endTime": 282.0,
    "text": "Sure, uh, let me get my, um, uh, bag."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.0,
    "endTime": 283.0,
    "text": "What a pro."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.0,
    "endTime": 286.0,
    "text": " He may be really shifty, but he's the best gosh darn surgeon I've ever met."
  }
]